        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>Genesis 3</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Gen-003-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ג והנחשׁ </foreign>
                            Da ol jylan edi jetiz ǯümlä kijigindän artyq ol düzniŋ ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            jaradty YWY Täŋri da ajtty ol ḫatynɣa farzam ki ajtty Täŋri
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            ašamaɣyn ǯümlä aɣačyndan ol baḫčanyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Gen-003-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol ḫatyn ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            jylanɣa jemišindän aɣačynyŋ ol baḫčanyŋ ašarmyz.</l>
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Gen-003-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וֺמפרי </foreign>
                            Anǯa jemišin-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            dän ol aɣačnyŋ ki ortasynda ol baḫčanyŋ ajtty Täŋri ašamaŋyz andan
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            da tijmäŋiz aŋar olmaja ölürsiz.</l>
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Gen-003-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol jylan ol ḫatynɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ölmä ölmässiz.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Gen-003-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כּי </foreign>
                            Anǯa bilir Täŋri ki ašaɣan günüŋizdä andan ačylyrlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            gözläriŋiz da olursyz malʾaḫlar gibi bilivčilär jaḫšyny da jamanny.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Gen-003-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותרא</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            Da fikir idti ol ḫatyn ki jaḫšydyr ol aɣač ašamaɣa da ki musančtyr
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            ol gözlärgä da ki suḫlančlydyr ol aɣač aŋlamaɣa da aldy jemišindän da ašady
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            da verdi daɣyn erinä ki birgäsinä da ašady.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Gen-003-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותּפקחנה </foreign>
                            Da ačyldylar gözläri
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ekisiniŋ da bildilär ki čyplaqtyrlar olar da tiktilär japraɣyn
                            inǯirlikniŋ da qyldylar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            gendilärinä fartuḫlar.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Gen-003-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וישׁמעו </foreign>
                            Da ešittilär sesin YWY Täŋriniŋ ki jürüjdir
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            baḫčada jelli gündä da jašyndy ol adam da ḫatyny aldyndan YWY Täŋriniŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            ortasynda aɣačynyŋ ol baḫčanyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Gen-003-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da čaqyrdy YWY Täŋri ol adam-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            ɣa da ajtty aŋar qajdasyn.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Gen-003-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da ajtty sesiŋni ešittim baḫčada
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            da qorqtym zire čyplaqtyrmen da jašyndym.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Gen-003-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty kim aŋlatty
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            saŋa ki čyplaqtyrsen ol aɣačtanmy ki tenbäḥ idtim saŋa ašamamaqqa
                            <milestone unit="page" n="7v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            andan ašadyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Gen-003-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty ol adam ol ḫatyn ki verdiŋ birgemä
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            ol verdi maŋa ol aɣačtan da ašadym.</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Gen-003-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty YWY Täŋri ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            ḫatynɣa ne bu qyldyŋ da ajtty ol ḫatyn ol jylan azɣyrdy meni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            da ašadym.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Gen-003-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty YWY Täŋri ol jylanɣa čünki qyldyŋ bu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            fenalyqny (eksik olasyn) qarɣyšlydyrsen ǯümlä ol tuvardan da ǯümlä
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            kijigindän ol düzniŋ qursaɣyŋ üstünä jürürsin da topraq ašarsyn ǯümlä
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            günlärindä dirlikleriŋniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Gen-003-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואיבה </foreign>
                            Da dušmanlyq qojarmyn araŋa da arasyna ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            ḫatynnyŋ da arasyna urluɣyŋnyŋ da arasyna urluɣunyŋ ol urar se<supplied
                                reason="lost">n</supplied>i<ref n="1" target="#Gen-003-fn1"
                                type="noteAnchor" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            bašqa da sen ysyryrsyn any ökčäsindän.</l>
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Gen-003-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">אל </foreign>
                            Ol ḫatynɣa ajtty köbäjtmä
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            köbäjtirmän emgägiŋni da ḥamläligiŋni emgäk bilän doɣurursyn evladlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            da eriŋä olur kilägiŋ da ol erklänir saŋa.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Gen-003-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ולאדם </foreign>
                            Da adamɣa ajtty čünki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ešittiŋ sözünä ḫatynyŋnyŋ da ašadyŋ ol aɣačtan ki tenbäḥ idtim saŋa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            demä ašamaɣyn andan qarɣyšlydyr ol jer seniŋ učun emgäk bilän ašarsyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            maḫsuluny ǯümlä günlärindä dirlikläriŋniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Gen-003-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וקוץ </foreign>
                            Da quvra da tegänäk bittirir
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            saŋa da ašarsyn otun ol düzniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Gen-003-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בזעת </foreign>
                            Teri bilen burnyŋnyŋ ašarsyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            ekmäk qajtqanyŋa degin ol topraqɣa ki andan alyndyŋ zira topraqdyr
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            sen da topraqqa qajtyrsyn.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Gen-003-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da atady ol adam adyn ḫatynynyŋ Ḥava
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            zira ol edi anasy ǯümlä diriniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Gen-003-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויעשׁ </foreign>
                            Da qyldy YWY Täŋri adamɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            da ḫatynyna deri gölmäklär da gijdirdi alarɣa.</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Gen-003-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Adonaj Tänri
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            muna ol adam fikirinǯä oldu bir gibi bizden bilmägä jaḫšyny da jamanny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            da endi olmaja sunar qolun da alyr daɣyn aɣačyndan da ol dirlikniŋ da
                            ašar da diri
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            olur dunjaɣa degin.</l>
                        <l n="23" xml:id="Gen-003-023"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וישׁלחהו </foreign>
                            Da sürdi any YWY Täŋri ɣanimätli baḫčadan išlämä-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ge ol topraqny ki alyndy oradan.</l>
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Gen-003-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויגרשׁ </foreign>
                            Da sürdi ol adamny da toḫtatty
                            <milestone unit="page" n="8r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            <seg type="commented" corresp="#Gen-003-seg001" />ilkindän
                                čyqmasynyŋ<anchor type="commented" xml:id="Gen-003-seg001" /><ref
                                n="2" target="#Gen-003-fn2" type="noteAnchor" /> ol Keruvlarny da
                            jyltyramaɣyn ol ajlana turɣan <supplied reason="lost"
                                >qyl</supplied>yčnyŋ<ref n="3" target="#Gen-003-fn3"
                                type="noteAnchor" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            saqlamaɣa jolun aɣačynyŋ ol dirlikniŋ.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn1" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: <emph>seŋi</emph>;
                            probably a scribal error. | BSMS 288: <emph>seni</emph>. | ADub.III.73:
                                <emph>seni</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn2" type="footnote">A mistranslation of the Biblical
                            Hebrew <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מִקֶּדֶם
                                לְגַן־עֵדֶן </foreign>
                            ‘from the east of the garden of Eden’. A similar mistranslation of the
                            word <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מִקֶּדֶם </foreign>
                            was previously mentioned in Gen 2:8. JSul.IV.02A: <emph>ilkinden
                                čyqmasynyn</emph> probably stands for ‘from the first (place) of his
                            leaving’ which refers the garden of Eden from where Adam and Eve had
                            been banished. |BSMS 288: <emph>kün doɣušy sartyn baɣyna
                            ʿEdenniŋ</emph>. | ADub.III.73:</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-003-fn3" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A:
                                <emph>lyqyčnyŋ</emph>; a scribal error. | BSMS 288:
                                <emph>qylyčnyŋ</emph>. | ADub.III.73: <emph>qylyčnyn</emph>.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
